      "text": "ゲームセンターでもダンスゲームをやってるのね\nあんなに目立つことして……まったくもう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like they're playing dance games at the game center too\nDoing something so conspicuous… it's ridiculous",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666658402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
