    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　あ、これ知ってるわ。クレーンゲームって\nいうのよね。あのぬいぐるみ、意外と可愛い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh‚ I know this. It's called\na claw machine. That plushie is surprisingly cute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0999991735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9198799133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
