      "text": "今日は葵の見張り役のつもりで来たけど……\nちょっとくらいなら私も……やってみようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came here to keep an eye on Aoi today…\nIt's just a little bit‚ can I… try it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5666658402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
