      "text": "何言ってるのよ！　どんな状況だって諦めなければ\n必ず道は開けるのよ！　私は負けないわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about! No matter what the situation‚ if you don't give up‚\na path will surely open up! I won't lose!",
